						<p><hi rend="bold">Chōḻa, Vikrama Chōḻa Year 3 = 1121 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>Records the construction of the temple, along with the <hi rend="italic">maḍaviḷāgam</hi> and flower garden, by Perumaṅgalam-uḍaiyāṉ <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Periyāṉ Tiruvaṉ for the merit of Araiyaṉ Kākkunāyakaṉalias Kaṉakarāyaṉ of Kōṉūr in Poyyiṟ-kūṟṟam in Rājādhirāja-vaḷanāḍu.</p>						

