<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī</hi> vikkirama coḻa tevaṟku yāṇṭu mū
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṉṟāvatu <hi rend="grantha">rājādhirāja</hi> vaḷanāṭṭu poyyiṟ kūṟ
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṟṟattu koṉūruṭaiyāṉ Araiyaṉ kākkunāyakaṉāṉa kaṉa
<lb n="4" break="no"/>karāyaṉ ceyvitta tirukkaṟṟaḷiyum Ittevar tirumaṭaivi
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ḷākamum tirunantaṉavaṉaṅkaḷum Akaḻipākkamāṉa vikkira
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ma coḻanallūrum kākkunāyaka viḷākamum viṭuvi
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ttāṉ kaṉakarāyarkku Āka Ittirukkaṟṟaḷiyum tanma
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ṅkaḷum ceyvittāṉ peyttalaipperumaṅka
<lb n="9" break="no"/>lam Uṭaiyāṉ periyāntiruvaṉ Āṉa ciṟutto
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ṇṭar§
</p>

